## ERROR TIPS

### Errors when using extracting but being too far
- Make sure to move to the target entity where you want to extract from before extracting items.

### Errors when placing into a tile which is occupied by another entity
- Ensure you can place an entity to a tile before attempting to place.

### Errors related to fuel supply
- The burner inserter at position (42.5, -80.5) frequently reports "NO_FUEL". Ensure that the inserter has a continuous supply of fuel to operate effectively.

### Errors with waiting for space in destination
- The burner inserter at position (43.5, -81.5) is often "WAITING_FOR_SPACE_IN_DESTINATION". Check the destination entity's inventory to ensure it has space to accept items.
